metadata.name: Huma
metadata.description:
Burn to emerge. Immortality and rebirth.
The mythological Phoenix disappears and reappears.
It can be found in much of ancient Eastern artwork from Sung Dynasty vases to Greek colosseums.
It also represents a symbol of the world being rebuilt after theÂ Second World War.

The legendary longevity of the Phoenix can be compared to the blockchain.
We are experiencing exponential transformative developments.
Blockchain and AI have fundamental changed the way we live, work, and relate to one another.

Here the motif is to sprout with life.
To be reborn from the remnants of the old.
Burn to emerge. Immortality and rebirth.
